Both Stetmann and protoss use terrazine to commune with "voices" in their heads. In the protoss' case, they commune with the dark god Amon.

"Little buddies" refers to the army of mechanical minions Stetmann created. This is a cultural reference to Avengers: Infinity War wherein Tony Stark states that Bruce Banner is embarrassing him in front of the wizards.
Bel'shir is the planet that Egon Stetmann was marooned on for many years.
Meatbag is a cultural reference to Bender from Futurama
